            "coding": [
              {
                "system": "urn:virpat:fhir:doc-type",
                "code": "patient-description"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "subject": {
          "reference": "urn:uuid:11111111-1111-4111-8111-111111111111"
        },
        "payload": [
          {
            "contentString": "{patientName} is a cheerful 6-year-old Czech girl with bright brown eyes and a slightly flushed face, currently looking tired and listless compared to her usual energetic self. She attends first grade at a local elementary school in Brno and enjoys drawing, playing with her younger brother, and attending weekly dance classes. She lives with her parents and a 3-year-old brother in a comfortable apartment in the city.\n\nOver the past three days, {patientName} has been complaining of a sore throat, runny nose with clear-to-slightly-yellow discharge, and a mild cough. She has been sneezing frequently and her mother noticed she was breathing through her mouth due to nasal congestion. {patientName} also complained of a stomach ache [SNOMED:J06.9], which her parents attributed to the general discomfort of being unwell. She has been eating poorly and drinking less than usual.\n\nHer temperature measured at home reached 38.3 °C. She has been more irritable than usual and has had difficulty sleeping due to nasal congestion [MEDDIALOG:J06.9:5]. Her mother brought her to the pediatric clinic when the symptoms did not improve after two days of rest and home remedies.\n\n{patientName} attends a daycare-like after-school program, and her mother reports that several other children in her class have had similar symptoms this week [MEDDIALOG:J06.9:0]. She is generally active and healthy, enjoys outdoor play in the park near their home, and has a well-balanced diet."
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "fullUrl": "urn:uuid:adbbf522-0f94-4da4-9759-25563b3b5571",
      "resource": {
        "resourceType": "Communication",
        "status": "completed",
        "text": {
